TY  - JOUR
TI  - Inflation and Asset Prices in an Exchange Economy
AU  - Danthine, Jean-Pierre
AU  - Donaldson, John B.
AB  - [This paper studies the pricing of common stocks in the context of a monetary, rational expectations equilibrium. Special attention is given to the relationship between inflation and asset returns.]
